    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>teriyaki glaze</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> (save some for garnish!) to the pan</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min further or until the sauce has coated the tofu nicely – this is your<strong> teriyaki tofu</strong></p>",
